      title: 'Mastering JavaScript Classes: A Comprehensive Guide',
      slug: 'mastering-javascript-classes-a-comprehensive-guide',
      views: 0,
      description:
        '# Mastering JavaScript Classes: A Comprehensive Guide\n\nJavaScriptâ€™da **class** â€“ bu **object yaratish uchun shablon**.\nES6â€™dan boshlab, `class` sintaksisi joriy qilindi va u **OOP (Object-Oriented Programming)** uslubini soddaroq yozishga imkon beradi.\n\n---\n\n## Class nima?\n\nClass â€“ bu:\n\n* **Property (xususiyatlar)**\n* **Method (funksiyalar)**\n  ni bir joyga jamlagan obyekt tuzilmasi.\n\nOddiy qilib aytganda: **object uchun blueprint**.\n\n---\n\n## Oddiy Class yaratish\n\n```javascript\nclass Person {\n  constructor(name, age) {\n    this.name = name\n    this.age = age\n  }\n\n  greet() {\n    console.log(`Hello, my name is ${this.name} and I\'m ${this.age} years old.`)\n  }\n}\n\nconst user = new Person("Asilbek", 23)\nuser.greet()\n// Output: Hello, my name is Asilbek and I\'m 23 years old.\n```\n\n---\n\n## Classda Constructor\n\n* `constructor()` â€“ yangi obyekt yaratilganda avtomatik ishlaydi.\n* Unda obyektning boshlangâ€˜ich qiymatlari oâ€˜rnatiladi.\n\n---\n\n## Class Methods\n\nMetodlar class ichida yoziladi va obyektga tegishli boâ€˜ladi.\n\n```javascript\nclass Calculator {\n  add(a, b) {\n    return a + b\n  }\n  multiply(a, b) {\n    return a * b\n  }\n}\n\nconst calc = new Calculator()\nconsole.log(calc.add(2, 3))      // 5\nconsole.log(calc.multiply(2, 3)) // 6\n```\n\n---\n\n## Inheritance (Meros olish)\n\nBir class boshqa classdan xususiyat va metodlarni **olishi** mumkin.\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  speak() {\n    console.log("Animal makes a sound")\n  }\n}\n\nclass Dog extends Animal {\n  speak() {\n    console.log("Dog barks")\n  }\n}\n\nconst dog = new Dog()\ndog.speak() // Dog barks\n```\n\n---\n\n## `super` kalit soâ€˜zi\n\nChild class ichida **parent class constructor/metodiga murojaat qilish** uchun ishlatiladi.\n\n```javascript\nclass Vehicle {\n  constructor(type) {\n    this.type = type\n  }\n}\n\nclass Car extends Vehicle {\n  constructor(type, brand) {\n    super(type) // parent constructor chaqirilmoqda\n    this.brand = brand\n  }\n}\n\nconst car = new Car("Car", "BMW")\nconsole.log(car.type, car.brand) // Car BMW\n```\n\n---\n\n## Getter va Setter\n\nPropertyâ€™larni boshqarish uchun maxsus metodlar.\n\n```javascript\nclass User {\n  constructor(name) {\n    this._name = name\n  }\n\n  get name() {\n    return this._name\n  }\n\n  set name(newName) {\n    this._name = newName\n  }\n}\n\nconst u = new User("Ali")\nconsole.log(u.name) // Ali\nu.name = "Vali"\nconsole.log(u.name) // Vali\n```\n\n---\n\n## Static Methods\n\nClassga tegishli metodlar boâ€˜lib, obyekt yaratmasdan chaqiriladi.\n\n```javascript\nclass MathUtils {\n  static square(x) {\n    return x * x\n  }\n}\n\nconsole.log(MathUtils.square(5)) // 25\n```\n\n---\n\n## Xulosa\n\n* **Class** â€“ obyekt yaratish uchun blueprint.\n* `constructor` â€“ boshlangâ€˜ich qiymatlarni belgilash uchun.\n* `extends` â€“ meros olish imkonini beradi.\n* `super` â€“ parent classâ€™ga murojaat qilish uchun.\n* `getter/setter` â€“ propertyâ€™larni boshqaradi.\n* `static` â€“ obyekt yaratmasdan metodlarni chaqirish uchun.\n\nJavaScript classlari yordamida kodni **tartibli, qayta ishlatiladigan va object-oriented** qilish mumkin. ',
